cdata.name: Bowhead Health
cdata.desc:
Bowhead is a company with a team of medical doctors, biochemistry and data scientists, software and robotics engineers, designers and wellness coaches.

By using Blockchain, health records can be inter-operable across different platforms, hospital systems and services, while remaining secure and up to date.

Bowheadbelieves that health data is some of the most valuable data in the world. Bowhead will use anonymized customer health data to add value, while ensuring data is protected using cryptography. Customers gain access to healthcare and may also benefit financially by leasing access to their data in an anonymized manner.
